name: LUCKY DIP!
description:
Choose your size and we'll send you a selection of goodies at a reduced price! All packs contain:

2 x tee/vest/mix
2 x accessories
Selection of stickers

Thats over £50 worth of merch for £35.99, saving you over 25%!!

name: Morte Portrait Tee by Tracy D
description: We're sure she was an effervescent beauty in her day but time takes it toll and now all she's good for is this morte portrait. It's printed in black, pink and green ink onto a white/grey Gildan soft-style t-shirt, the size photographed is medium. All our clothing and accessories are unisex, we don't discriminate. This t-shirt is designed by Tracy D, artist at Kings Cross Tattoo Parlour, London. Click through to our artist page to read more about her! Or here to buy more of her designs.

name: Woman Warrior Vest by Dave Olteanu
description: If you like to be a bit controversial, this is the tee for you. Oh and if you like hot women too... Printed in black and red ink onto a white Fruit of the Loom vest, the size photographed is small. All our clothing and accessories are unisex, we don't discriminate. This t-shirt is designed by Dave Olteanu, artist at STR Body Modifications, NSW, Australia. Click through to our artist page to read more about him! Or here to buy more of his designs.

name: White Knight Tee by Phil Hatchet Yau
description:
To paraphrase Bonnie Tyler - this white knight is also the fiery stead!

Words can't describe our excitement when Phil Hatchet Yau agreed to do a design for us - his work blows us away with his distinct style and perfect execution. He is currently working in Downtown San Diego, CA.

See his body of work at philhatchetyau.com/

Printed in white and red ink onto a black Gildan soft-style t-shirt, the size photographed is medium. All our clothing and accessories are unisex, we don't discriminate.

name: Logo Snapback by Pastilliam
description: Our new logo embroidered on to Yupoong snapback hats, design by Pastilliam. We have the option of full black, or black with gray peak. Both options have green lining under the peak.
